bilingual.source: Your survival. How's that for a reason?

bilingual.source: Survival on Earth is a surprisingly tricky business.
bilingual.target: 在地球上幸存下来，这是一件非常微妙的事。

bilingual.source: In fact the entire system depends upon these processes for its survival.
bilingual.target: 事实上，整个群落倚靠这些过程来幸存下去。

bilingual.source: The Architect - There are levels of survival we are prepared to accept.
bilingual.target: 设计师:我们已经作好了接受任何幸存程度的准备.

bilingual.source: Without that, we couldn't maintain the temperature necessary for our survival.
bilingual.target: 如果没有肌肉，我们无法保持所需的体温，从而也难以幸存。

bilingual.source: Just one of the six men on board survived—a crew member who had chosen to sleep with his own personal survival suit stowed safely by his bed.
bilingual.target: 最终，大峡谷号在风浪中倾覆沉没，六名船员中只有一人幸存——因为这名幸存的船员将自己的救生服就放在枕头边。

bilingual.source: We are Hubble's only chance for survival, but a mission to save the telescope can be perilous.
bilingual.target: 我们是让哈勃能幸存的唯一希望，但修复它的过程会很危险。

bilingual.source: Shinra may have appeared finished at this point but for the miraculous survival of Rufus.
bilingual.target: 此时,要不是鲁弗斯奇迹般地幸存下来,神罗貌似就已经破产了.

bilingual.source: Due to the human heart, some species beloved of the human race will be assisted for survival.
bilingual.target: 由于人类的爱心，一些被人类喜爱的动物种类将会被帮助，幸存下来。

bilingual.source: Chris Hadfield talked so eloquently about fear and about the odds of success, and indeed the odds of survival.
bilingual.target: 克里斯?哈菲尔德痛陈了其中的恐惧以及成功与幸存的几率。

list.abstract: 《Survival》是英国乐队Muse演唱的歌曲。由Matthew Bellamy作词、作曲，收录在Muse 2012年9月发行的专辑《The 2nd Law》中。 英国Muse缪斯乐队的全新单曲《Survival（生存）》被钦定为2012年伦敦奥运会主题曲！将在运动员入场及颁奖仪式上播放。这支乐队于1994年在英国德文郡的Teignmouth镇创立。乐风融合了独立摇滚、前卫摇滚、重金属音乐、古典音乐与电音。在Muse的这三位成员刚刚聚到一起开始正式组乐队的时候，他们都只有13岁。

yingyinNormal.en: But most of all, these patriots knew to remain loyal to each other because their survival depended on it in a dangerous, new land.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但最重要的是，这些爱国者们保持对彼此的忠诚，因为他们能在那片危险的新大陆上幸存下来都是源于此。

yingyinNormal.en: Chances of survival are dwindling to single digits now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 存活的机率下降到个位数了。

yingyinNormal.en: Our survival demands total commitment to the destruction of the enemy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要想生存下去就必须全面剿灭敌人。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone on this base, every one of you, is fighting for survival. That's a fact!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个基地里的所有人都在为生存而战，这是个事实。

yingyinNormal.en: Today, the empire is still divided in three, and our very survival is threatened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天下三分，益州疲弊，此诚危急存亡之秋也，

yingyinNormal.en: Genes that result in a greater variety of immunities may give offspring a major survival advantage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 免疫能力多元的基因可能给后代重要的存活优势。

yingyinNormal.en: What was that? I mean why are we here? What are we doing this for? No one said survival was fun. Nothing is fun.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说什么? 我们为什么在这儿? 我们做这些又是为了什么? 没人说生存很有趣。没什么是有趣的。

yingyinNormal.en: The foods we crave are often high in fat and calories. that's an evolutionary survival tactic built into our genes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们渴望的食物通常含有大量热量。这是进化过程中根治在我们，基因中的特性。

yingyinNormal.en: Say, buddy, not to cast aspersions on your survival instincts or nothing, but haven't mammoths pretty much gone extinct?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不要用你的生存本能妖言惑众，不过长毛象不是快绝种了吗?

yingyinNormal.en: For the record, we had an Aircraft Systems Team on this investigation. Also Aircraft Structures, MRT, Aircraft Performance, ATC, Wildlife Factors, Survival Factors and Emergency Response.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先说明，我们有飞机系统小组参与这起调查，还有飞机结构组，维护检修组，飞机性能组，空中交通管制，野生动物因素，存活因素，应急响应。
